data.description: PRICE REDUCED PLUS $4,000 IN CONCESSIONS TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS!!!  NEW ROOF, SCREENS, GUTTERS AND LIVING ROOM PAINT! This former model home is like new. Just feel the warmth when you enter the front door. Enjoy your mornings or evenings on the front porch or the cozy covered back patio with an electric awning. Granite counter tops and island in kitchen; walk in pantry; tile back splash with beautiful maple cabinets; the study has wood floors, built in bookcase and french doors. Carpet, wood and tile floors throughout; master bath has large corner whirlpool tub, separate shower and double vanities. In ground sprinkler system. There is a LARGE walk in storm shelter in the garage:  it can be left where it is; moved to one side; moved to the front of the garage or removed if not wanted. Seller will do as you wish.  (Refrigerator, washer and dryer negotiable).  Enjoy the amenities that Valencia offers: multiple parks, 3 ponds stocked with fish, walking trails, splash pads, basketball court and more.  Easy access to Hefner Parkway and Kilpatrick turnpike.
